OL,3,CSavannah Guthrie offers $1 million
OL,4,Creward for return of her missing mother
OL,6,FUS news anchor Savannah Guthrie posted
OL,7,Fa video to her Instagram on Tuesday,
OL,8,Foffering a $1 million reward for
OL,9,Finformation leading to the return of
OL,10,Fher missing mother
OL,12,FThe family of Nancy Guthrie, who has
OL,13,Fbeen missing for more than three
OL,14,Fweeks, is offering up to $1 million
OL,15,Ffor information leading to her return.
OL,17,FIt's been 23 days since Savannah
OL,18,FGuthrie's mother vanished from her
OL,19,Fdesert home in the middle of the night.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
