OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1771981383
OL,3,CSavannah Guthrie offers $1 million
OL,4,Creward for return of her missing mother
OL,6,FThe 'Today' host said in a video
OL,7,Fposted to her Instagram on Tuesday
OL,8,Fthat her 84-year-old mother "may
OL,9,Falready be gone".
OL,11,FShe said: "But we need to know where
OL,12,Fshe is. We need her to come home. For
OL,13,Fthat reason, we are offering a family
OL,14,Freward of up to $1 million for any
OL,15,Finformation that leads us to her
OL,16,Frecovery."
OL,18,FThe money is in addition to the FBI's
OL,19,F$100,000 reward for information about
OL,20,FNancy Guthrie.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
