OL,3,CSavannah Guthrie offers $1 million
OL,4,Creward for return of her missing mother
OL,6,FThe reward announcement ends more than
OL,7,Fa week of silence from the Guthrie
OL,8,Ffamily, who had been posting regular
OL,9,Fvideo updates.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FInvestigative updates from authorities
OL,17,Fhave also slowed as the search enters
OL,18,Fits fourth week, though the case
OL,19,Fcontinues to draw national interest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
