OL,3,CSavannah Guthrie offers $1 million
OL,4,Creward for return of her missing mother
OL,6,FSavannah Guthrie added in the video:
OL,7,F"We still believe. We still believe.
OL,8,FWe still believe that she can come
OL,9,Fhome. Hope against hope, as my sister
OL,10,Fsays, we are blowing on the embers of
OL,11,Fhope."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/4
